{"tid":454121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哈囉喂老蘭多麗鬼　新款汽車攔截器首登場","createTime":"2017-10-31T23:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T08:43:56.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"949156d67eaf7515b3d792af7e8a4d4dc849b826","tid":454121,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=c29d58ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哈囉喂老蘭多麗鬼。(袁志豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=9a83f192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人人悉心扮鬼扮怪。(袁志豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_03b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=1ba694b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在人群聚集點放置組裝式汽車攔截器。(袁志豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=2abea3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬聖節到了，各式鬼怪急不及待在蘭桂坊上穿梭往來。(袁志豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_05b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=ab9bc6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一眾嘩鬼逼爆蘭桂坊。(袁志豪攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_06b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=f3856fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人在蘭桂坊搵鬼「集郵」。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_07b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=72a00aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有韓國來的旅客來蘭桂坊感受氣氛。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_08b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=91b50123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論男女都盛裝打扮。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_09b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=10906404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人帶齊整套化妝用品在大街即席變身。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_10b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_10b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=e633ad93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驚嚇程度爆燈的女鬼。(黃雄攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_11b.jpg?20171101050942\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001_11b.jpg%3F20171101050942&h=6716c8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方貼出蘭桂坊一帶封路安排，其fb小編更揚言想落去玩番晚。(香港警察fb)<br />\n<br />\n一年一度哈囉喂又到啦！除了去主題公園渡過一個觸目驚心的晚上，還可以選擇與友人到酒吧林立的中環蘭桂坊「摸吓酒杯底、睇吓嘩鬼」，盡情狂歡一晚，甚至連警隊fb小編亦不怕老闆詐型，公開留言話︰「如果收到工，小編今晚都想落去蘭桂坊玩返(番)晚」，同時又提醒市民留意該處在今天(31日)傍晚6時起將有多個封路措施，並指警方會因應人群聚集情況而作進一步封路安排。<br />\n<br />\n記者晚上7時許到達蘭桂坊，不少店舖均已換上應節的裝飾，例如南瓜、蜘蛛網及蝙蝠等，而悉心裝扮的嚇人鬼怪和俏女郎已急不及待在大街上穿梭往來，更大方地任由途人駐足拍攝，部分人則帶齊整套化妝用品在大街即席變身，素人鬼怪在鏡頭之下，個個都變成明星模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n踏入晚上8時許，蘭桂坊內的大街小巷早已逼得水洩不通。同時，警方首次在皇后大道中、雲咸街及德己立街等人群聚集點，放置組裝式汽車攔截器，以防止有汽車衝入人群的恐襲事件。據了解，基於過去2年，歐洲多處發生汽車衝入人群的恐襲事件，針對有關問題，警方從外國購入有關路障設施，並派出數百名反恐人員到場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人晚上表示，目前沒有具體情報顯示香港可能成為恐怖襲擊的目標，本港受到恐怖襲擊的威脅程度仍然維持在「中度」水平；而今晚警方在蘭桂芳附近的街道設置「組裝式汽車攔截器」及調派反恐特勤隊進行巡邏，並非有情報顯示該處可能成為襲擊目標。事實上，警方不時會調派人員包括反恐特勤隊作高姿態的軍裝巡邏。同時因應實際行動需要，購入合適的裝備。警隊亦定期進行反恐訓練及跨機構演習，以測試及強化應變計劃及能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fbkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1QycPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ac2db5ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bkn-20171031190950917-1031_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"0daa90cf10f9f1c9493009e78d1e8ddf3c430485","tid":454121,"uid":47147,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20e6751eecaba1501bba2c2776023e0097cb3d7d","tid":454121,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T23:54:36.000Z","msg":"最尾果張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d7c1f4a87719304c11df1b32ad52813a599162","tid":454121,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c